    <string name="onboarding_title_1">1. Works in the Shadows</string>
    <string name="onboarding_desc_1">TapTranslate doesn\'t have a main app you need to open daily. It operates uniquely as a hidden context button for max speed.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_title_2">2. How to use it?</string>
    <string name="onboarding_desc_2">Highlight any text you type, click the 3-dots option menu, and select TapTranslate to convert it instantly.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_title_3">3. 100% Local and Private</string>
    <string name="onboarding_desc_3">A one-time 30MB dictionary download is required. After that, all translations happen internally, fully offline.</string>
